OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1772223642
OL,3,CReform UK reports alleged 'family
OL,4,Cvoting' in by-election to the police
OL,6,FReform UK has gone to the police to
OL,7,Freport cases of "family voting" in the
OL,8,FGorton and Denton by-election.
OL,10,FIt comes after election observer group
OL,11,FDemocracy Volunteers warned it had
OL,12,Fwitnessed "concerningly high levels"
OL,13,Fof family voting - an illegal practice
OL,14,Fwhere two voters use one polling booth
OL,15,Fand potentially direct each other on
OL,16,Fvoting.
OL,26,@oD@QOUoD@_O]tD@KOUtD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/15
