CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1772223642
OL,3,CReform UK reports alleged 'family
OL,4,Cvoting' in by-election to the police
OL,6,FNigel Farage has also called for an
OL,7,Finvestigation into breaches of ballot
OL,8,Fsecrecy to be launched by the
OL,9,FElectoral Commission, which had
OL,10,Fdirected those who think an offence
OL,11,Fhas been committed to go to police.
OL,13,FMr Farage claimed there was "sectarian
OL,14,Fvoting and cheating" in the election
OL,15,Fafter his party came second to the
OL,16,FGreens, who dismissed the remarks as a
OL,17,Fbid to undermine the result.
OL,26,@uD@]OUvD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1772223642
OL,3,CReform UK reports alleged 'family
OL,4,Cvoting' in by-election to the police
OL,6,FMr Farage said: "Reform has today
OL,7,Freported the many cases of 'family
OL,8,Fvoting' to the electoral commission
OL,9,Fand the police.
OL,11,F"What was witnessed yesterday is
OL,12,Fdeeply concerning and raises serious
OL,13,Fquestions about the integrity of the
OL,14,Fdemocratic process in predominantly
OL,15,FMuslim areas.
OL,17,F"If this is what was happening at
OL,18,Fpolling stations, just imagine the
OL,19,Fpotential for coercion with postal
OL,20,Fvotes.
OL,26,@nD@QOUsD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1772223642
OL,3,CReform UK reports alleged 'family
OL,4,Cvoting' in by-election to the police
OL,6,F"If action isn't taken now, then we
OL,7,Fwill ensure it is after the next
OL,8,Fgeneral election."
OL,10,FGreater Manchester Police has
OL,11,Fconfirmed a report has been made. It
OL,12,Fsaid: "We are in the process of
OL,13,Freviewing this report and will provide
OL,14,Fa further update in due course."
OL,16,FA Greens spokesperson said: "This is
OL,17,Fan attempt to undermine the democratic
OL,18,Fresult and is straight out of the
OL,19,FTrump playbook.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@RO]tD@GOUvD@`O]xD@]OU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
