PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1772223642
OL,3,CReform UK reports alleged 'family
OL,4,Cvoting' in by-election to the police
OL,6,F"We've just won a historic by-election
OL,7,Fby a comfortable margin.
OL,9,F"We've shown the country that Greens
OL,10,Fcan beat Reform, despite their big
OL,11,Fbusiness donations."
OL,13,FThe Green Party candidate Hannah
OL,14,FSpencer claimed a majority of 4,402
OL,15,Fvotes, overturning a Labour majority
OL,16,Fof more than 13,000.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUsD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
