FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1772223642
OL,3,CReform UK reports alleged 'family
OL,4,Cvoting' in by-election to the police
OL,6,FAfter Democracy Volunteers raised
OL,7,Fconcerns over family voting,
OL,8,FManchester City Council said no issues
OL,9,Fhad been reported and that it was
OL,10,F"extremely disappointing" the group
OL,11,Fhad waited until after the close of
OL,12,Fpolls to make the claims.
OL,14,FDemocracy Volunteers' director John
OL,15,FAult said that it "is a normal
OL,16,Finternational standard not to issue a
OL,17,Fcomment until after voting has
OL,18,Ffinished" and that "we posed questions
OL,19,Fabout family voting in several polling
OL,20,Fstations".
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@YO]wD@SOUzD@IO]zD@TOU|D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1772223642
OL,3,CReform UK reports alleged 'family
OL,4,Cvoting' in by-election to the police
OL,6,FDemocracy Volunteers said its
OL,7,Fobservers saw family voting in 15 of
OL,8,Fthe 22 polling stations observed. They
OL,9,Fsaid they saw family voting affecting
OL,10,F12% of voters observed when they
OL,11,Fvisited polling stations, compared to
OL,12,F1% in the Runcorn and Helsby by-
OL,13,Felection.
OL,15,FShadow local government secretary
OL,16,FJames Cleverly has also contacted the
OL,17,FElectoral Commission requesting a full
OL,18,Finquiry.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1772223642
OL,3,CReform UK reports alleged 'family
OL,4,Cvoting' in by-election to the police
OL,6,FThe Conservative frontbencher said:
OL,7,F"The report published by Democracy
OL,8,FVolunteers on the Gorton and Denton
OL,9,Fparliamentary by-election says
OL,10,Felectoral offences were committed.
OL,12,F"It is completely unacceptable for
OL,13,Fanyone to be watched or pressured
OL,14,Finside a polling station."
OL,16,FThe Electoral Commission said
OL,17,Fobservers are expected to raise
OL,18,Fpotential fraud or irregularities at
OL,19,Fthe polls "on the spot" and that
OL,20,Felectoral offences are a police matter.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUvD@ZO]{D@KOU{D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
