OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1772223642
OL,3,CReform UK reports alleged 'family
OL,4,Cvoting' in by-election to the police
OL,6,FAsked if the Prime Minister had
OL,7,Fconcerns about the allegations, a No
OL,8,F10 spokesperson said: "The law is the
OL,9,Flaw and it's essential that electors
OL,10,Fcan cast their votes in secret without
OL,11,Fany risk of coercion.
OL,13,F"Obviously, if anyone has witnessed
OL,14,Fcoercion, they should discuss that
OL,15,Fmatter with their local elections team
OL,16,For the police."
OL,18,FReform UK has also raised wider
OL,19,Fconcerns around the poll.
OL,26,@pD@WOUuD@AOUxD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
