PN,39311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1772223642
OL,3,CReform UK reports alleged 'family
OL,4,Cvoting' in by-election to the police
OL,6,FIn a post overnight, Reform UK leader
OL,7,FMr Farage said: "This election was a
OL,8,Fvictory for sectarian voting and
OL,9,Fcheating."
OL,11,FAsked what he meant, his party's
OL,12,Fchairman David Bull told Sky News:
OL,13,F"The Green Party appealed to the
OL,14,FMuslim vote. 33% of that constituency
OL,15,Fis Muslim. They printed their leaflets
OL,16,Fin Urdu."
OL,18,FHe added that his party were also
OL,19,Fworried about family voting and postal
OL,20,Fvotes.
OL,26,@oD@QOUqD@JO]uD@AOUxD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1772223642
OL,3,CReform UK reports alleged 'family
OL,4,Cvoting' in by-election to the police
OL,6,FMr Bull said: "I'm worried about
OL,7,Felectoral fraud generally.
OL,9,F"Am I saying it changed the outcome of
OL,10,Fthis election?
OL,12,F"No, but I think what we do need to do
OL,13,Fis to make sure that these elections,
OL,14,Fevery election, is free, democratic
OL,15,Fand fair."
OL,26,@nD@OOUqD@AOUtD@AOUwD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
