OL,3,CReform UK reports alleged 'family
OL,4,Cvoting' in by-election to the police
OL,6,FGreen Party leader Zack Polanski
OL,7,Frejected any accusations of
OL,8,Fsectarianism as he was asked whether
OL,9,Fhe had deliberately fuelled anger
OL,10,Famong Muslim voters with leaflets
OL,11,Ffeaturing images of Sir Keir Starmer
OL,12,Fshaking hands with Indian Prime
OL,13,FMinister Narendra Modi.
OL,15,FWhile he accepted that Sir Keir needed
OL,16,Fto speak to world leaders for
OL,17,Fdiplomatic reasons, he said the
OL,18,Fmaterials showed his "pally"
OL,19,Frelationship with them.
OL,26,@zD@VOUzD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39314
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1772223642
OL,3,CReform UK reports alleged 'family
OL,4,Cvoting' in by-election to the police
OL,6,F"Modi is an authoritarian who, whether
OL,7,Fyou're Jewish, Muslim or you're non
OL,8,Ffaith, (you) should have problems with
OL,9,Fthe authoritarianism that Keir Starmer
OL,10,Fis working with in cosy ways, that's
OL,11,Fvery different to having diplomatic
OL,12,Frelations ... I absolutely deny
OL,13,Fplaying to racism," he told BBC Radio
OL,14,F4's Today programme.
OL,16,FConservative Party leader Kemi
OL,17,FBadenoch said Labour, the Greens and
OL,18,FReform had all stirred up "grievance
OL,19,Fpolitics".
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@SO]zD@[OU{D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39315
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1772223642
OL,3,CReform UK reports alleged 'family
OL,4,Cvoting' in by-election to the police
OL,6,F"If you stir up grievance politics
OL,7,Fbetween groups based on religion or
OL,8,Frace, as Labour have done for decades,
OL,9,Fas Reform are seeking to do, and as
OL,10,Fthe Greens have done successfully in
OL,11,Fthis by-election, you are pitting
OL,12,Fneighbours against each other and you
OL,13,Fstart to unravel the culture of
OL,14,Ftolerance that makes Britain great,"
OL,15,Fshe said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/15
